{"id":632003,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/01/【新闻连连看】伊朗承认意外击落客机-vs-驳斥击落/","date":"2020-01-11T10:05:28Z","modified":"2020-01-11T10:05:28Z","title":"【新闻连连看】伊朗承认意外击落客机 VS 驳斥击落客机说","content":"<p><strong>环球时报｜伊朗承认意外击落乌克兰载176人飞机：人为失误   </strong></p>\n<p>发布时间：2020-01-11 11:50:09</p>\n<p>【环球网快讯】据美联社刚刚消息，伊朗国家电视台援引军方声明说，伊朗无意中击落了失事的乌克兰客机。声明于当地时间11日早上发布，并将飞机被击落归咎于“人为失误”。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_632004\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/2020_0111_da2df9d5p00q3xcb0000yc000vn00aec.png\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-632004\" class=\"wp-image-632004\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/2020_0111_da2df9d5p00q3xcb0000yc000vn00aec.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"181\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/2020_0111_da2df9d5p00q3xcb0000yc000vn00aec.png 1139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/2020_0111_da2df9d5p00q3xcb0000yc000vn00aec-300x99.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/2020_0111_da2df9d5p00q3xcb0000yc000vn00aec-1024x336.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/2020_0111_da2df9d5p00q3xcb0000yc000vn00aec-768x252.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/2020_0111_da2df9d5p00q3xcb0000yc000vn00aec-1080x355.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-632004\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">美联社报道截图</p></div>\n<p>本月8日，乌克兰国际航空公司一架波音737型客机在德黑兰霍梅尼国际机场附近坠毁，机上167名乘客和9名机组人员无一生还。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/2020_0111_f5bba776p00q3xcb000fpc000gx009sc.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-632005\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/2020_0111_f5bba776p00q3xcb000fpc000gx009sc.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"318\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/2020_0111_f5bba776p00q3xcb000fpc000gx009sc.png 609w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/2020_0111_f5bba776p00q3xcb000fpc000gx009sc-300x173.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>环球时报｜伊朗驳斥导弹打客机说  </strong></p>\n<p>发布时间：2020-01-11</p>\n<p>报道内容选摘：</p>\n<blockquote><p>德黑兰方面表示，现在下定论为时尚早，伊朗已邀请美国、加拿大、法国、瑞典和乌克兰派代表共同调查事故，“一切都必须等黑匣子打开才能做结论”。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EN-t6yAUEAIw6-8.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-632024\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EN-t6yAUEAIw6-8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EN-t6yAUEAIw6-8.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EN-t6yAUEAIw6-8-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/01/EN-t6yAUEAIw6-8-768x432.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,38895,38912,38923],"tags":[14334,8890,39661,14004]}